==========================================================
AEGISNET PHASE 3
MITRE ATT&CK SPATIAL GRAPHRAG (THE MAPPER)
==========================================================

GOAL:
-----
Phase 3 builds a dynamic, searchable map of the entire 
corporate network, linking servers, subnets, and 
vulnerabilities so the AI can understand lateral movement.


WHY PHASE 3 EXISTS:
-------------------

Phase 1 & 2 can tell us:

    "Ramnit Malware just hit Server X."

But they cannot tell us:

    "What other servers is Server X connected to?
     Does it hold critical data? 
     How can the attacker move from here?"

Phase 3 provides this vital context.


